msgid ""
"The idea behind this flow controller is to have a linear relationship between :"
"math:`Q` and :math:`h_L` (remember that :math:`h_L` is equal to :math:`\\Delta "
"h` when we apply the head loss trick), which can be written as :math:`Q "
"\\propto h_L`. Here, :math:`Q` is the flow of chemicals out of the flexible "
"tube, and :math:`h_L` is the elevation difference between the water level in "
"the CHT and the end of the flexible tube."
